eading mt-3 has-text-align-center\">A Proven Database for Your Mission-Critical Operations<\/h2>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">MariaDB Enterprise Platform is engineered to deliver best-in-class performance, data security, replication, clustering and high availability for production workloads. MariaDB Enterprise Platform empowers modern data strategies with an end-to-end database solution, delivering consistent performance and unwavering stability for mission-critical applications in demanding environments. Eliminate database sprawl and simplify your data landscape by running all your workloads in a single, robust MariaDB environment, powered by open source technology and fortified with enterprise-grade reliability, security and support.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/mariadb-icon {\"iconClass\":\"icon-globe\",\"iconSize\":\"display-1\",\"iconColor\":\"sublime-gradient\",\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"mb-0\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-mariadb-icon d-flex justify-content-center mb-0\"><span class=\"icon-globe display-1 text-sublime-gradient\"><\/span><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/mariadb-icon -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":4,\"className\":\"mt-\"} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading mt-3 has-text-align-center mt-\">Run MariaDB Anywhere<\/h4>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">MariaDB Enterprise Platform is engineered for any environment, from on premises to any cloud \u2013 private, public, hybrid or multicloud \u2013 delivering ultimate deployment flexibility.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-section {\"hPadding\":\"py-0\"} -->\n<section class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-content-section py-0\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row \"><!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/conte