nd streamlined HTAP environment. MariaDB Exa, an optional component, enables highly performant multi-node processing, providing unparalleled HTAP performance for large-scale, complex queries.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column -->\n\n<!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column {\"columnSize\":\"6\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-content-column col-12 position-relative col-lg-6\"><div class=\"h-100 position-relative z-1 column-content-wrap text-center align-items-center\"><!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/mariadb-icon {\"iconClass\":\"icon-search\",\"iconSize\":\"display-5\",\"iconColor\":\"icon-gradient\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-mariadb-icon d-flex justify-content-center\"><span class=\"icon-search display-5 text-icon-gradient\"><\/span><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/mariadb-icon -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"h4\",\"textColor\":\"deep-ocean\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading mt-3 h4 has-deep-ocean-color has-text-color text-deep-ocean\">Native vector embedded search<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Lorem Ipsum ....\"} -->\n<p>With MariaDB\u2019s native vector embedded search, implement retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) to build AI applications that deliver accurate and contextually rich results, eliminating the complexity of integrating vector only databases. MCP Server and AI RAG make implementing custom GenAI applications simpler.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column --><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-section -->\n\n<!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-section {\"hPadding\":\"py-3\"} -->\n<section class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-content-section py-3\"><div class=\"container\"><div cl