DB\u2019s hybrid transactional and analytical processing (HTAP). Seamlessly blend row and columnar storage to infuse real-time, powerful analytics into standard transactional workflows.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column -->\n\n<!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column {\"columnSize\":\"6\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-content-column col-12 position-relative col-lg-6\"><div class=\"h-100 position-relative z-1 column-content-wrap text-center align-items-center\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4,\"className\":\"h4\",\"textColor\":\"deep-ocean\"} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading mt-3 h4 has-deep-ocean-color has-text-color text-deep-ocean\">Artificial Intelligence\/Machine Learning<\/h4>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Lorem Ipsum ....\"} -->\n<p>By integrating vector embedded search directly into its database engine, MariaDB Enterprise Platform streamlines your data stack, eliminating the need for separate vector databases and reducing complexity.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column --><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-section -->\n\n<!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-section {\"hPadding\":\"py-2\"} -->\n<section class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-content-section py-2\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row \"><!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column {\"columnSize\":\"3\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-content-column col-12 position-relative col-lg-3\"><div class=\"h-100 position-relative z-1 column-content-wrap text-center align-items-center\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4,\"className\":\"h4\",\"textColor\":\"deep-ocean\"} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading mt-3 h4 has-deep-ocean-color has-text-color text-deep-ocean\"><\/h4>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\