locks-content-section py-3\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row \"><!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column {\"columnSize\":\"4\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-content-column col-12 position-relative col-lg-4\"><div class=\"h-100 position-relative z-1 column-content-wrap text-center align-items-center\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4,\"className\":\"h4\",\"textColor\":\"deep-ocean\"} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading mt-3 h4 has-deep-ocean-color has-text-color text-deep-ocean\">Transactional<\/h4>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Lorem Ipsum ....\"} -->\n<p>Experience high-performance, reliable and scalable transaction processing with MariaDB. Deploy as a replicated or clustered database (relational, document or hybrid) using modern SQL and leverage seamless Oracle Database compatibility.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column -->\n\n<!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column {\"columnSize\":\"4\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-content-column col-12 position-relative col-lg-4\"><div class=\"h-100 position-relative z-1 column-content-wrap text-center align-items-center\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4,\"className\":\"h4\",\"textColor\":\"deep-ocean\"} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading mt-3 h4 has-deep-ocean-color has-text-color text-deep-ocean\">Analytical<\/h4>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Lorem Ipsum ....\"} -->\n<p>Unlock real-time insights with MariaDB\u2019s analytical capabilities. Deploy as a standalone or distributed data warehouse, utilizing columnar storage for interactive analytics and leveraging cost-effective cloud object storage.<br><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column -->\n\n<!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column {\"columnSize\":\"4\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-content-column col-12 position-relative col-lg-4\"><div class=\"h-100 position-relative z-1 column-content-wrap text-center align-items-center\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4,\"className\":\"h4\",\"textColor\":\"deep-ocean\"} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading mt-3 h4 has-deep-ocean-color has-text-color text-deep-ocean\">Semi-Structured<\/h4>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Lorem Ipsum ....\"} -->\n<p>With a comprehensive set of JSON functions, MariaDB enables efficient processing, querying and manipulation of JSON documents. These functions allow you to extract specific data, modify structures and seamlessly integrate JSON data with traditional relational data.<br><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column --><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-section -->\n\n<!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-section {\"hPadding\":\"py-3\"} -->\n<section class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-content-section py-3\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row \"><!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column {\"columnSize\":\"6\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-content-column col-12 position-relative col-lg-6\"><div class=\"h-100 position-relative z-1 column-content-wrap text-center align-items-center\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4,\"className\":\"h4\",\"textColor\":\"deep-ocean\"} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading mt-3 h4 has-deep-ocean-color has-text-color text-deep-ocean\">Mixed<\/h4>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Lorem Ipsum ....\"} -->\n<p>Deliver intelligent customer experiences with MariaDB\u2019s hybrid transactional and analytical processing (HTAP). Seamlessly blend row and columnar storage to infuse real-time, powerful analytics into standard transactional workflows.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column -->\n\n<!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column {\"columnSize\":\"6\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-content-column col-12 position-relative col-lg-6\"><div class=\"h-100 position-relative z-1 column-content-wrap text-center align-items-center\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4,\"className\":\"h4\",\"textColor\":\"deep-ocean\"} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading mt-3 h4 has-deep-ocean-color has-text-color text-deep-ocean\">Artificial Intelligence\/Machine Learning<\/h4>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Lorem Ipsum ....\"} -->\n<p>By integrating vector embedded search directly into its database engine, MariaDB Enterprise Platform streamlines your data stack, eliminating the need for separate vector databases and reducing complexity.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column --><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-section -->\n\n<!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-section {\"hPadding\":\"py-2\"} -->\n<section class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-content-section py-2\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row \"><!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column {\"columnSize\":\"3\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-content-column col-12 position-relative col-lg-3\"><div class=\"h-100 position-relative z-1 column-content-wrap text-center align-items-center\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4,\"className\":\"h4\",\"textColor\":\"deep-ocean\"} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading mt-3 h4 has-deep-ocean-color has-text-color text-deep-ocean\"><\/h4>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Lorem Ipsum ....\"} -->\n<p><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column -->\n\n<!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column {\"columnSize\":\"6\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-con