 search and developer-first tooling directly into your database.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column {\"columnSize\":\"4\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-content-column col-12 position-relative col-lg-4\"><div class=\"h-100 position-relative z-1 column-content-wrap text-center align-items-center\"><!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/mariadb-icon {\"iconClass\":\"icon-tech-support\",\"iconSize\":\"display-3\",\"iconColor\":\"blue-azure\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-mariadb-icon d-flex justify-content-center\"><span class=\"icon-tech-support display-3 text-blue-azure\"><\/span><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/mariadb-icon -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"h4\",\"textColor\":\"deep-ocean\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading mt-3 h4 has-deep-ocean-color has-text-color text-deep-ocean\">Developer and DBA Copilot Agents<\/h3>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Lorem Ipsum ....\"} -->\n<p>Boost productivity with embedded AI agents that handle everything from Text-to-SQL generation to proactive performance tuning.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column -->\n\n<!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/content-column {\"columnSize\":\"4\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-content-column col-12 position-relative col-lg-4\"><div class=\"h-100 position-relative z-1 column-content-wrap text-center align-items-center\"><!-- wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/mariadb-icon {\"iconClass\":\"icon-fast-analytics\",\"iconSize\":\"display-3\",\"iconColor\":\"blue-azure\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-mariadb-content-blocks-mariadb-icon d-flex justify-content-center\"><span class=\"icon-fast-analytics display-3 text-blue-azure\"><\/span><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:mariadb-content-blocks\/mariadb-icon -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"l